    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "You can toss sneezing powder at an adjacent creature as an Interact action. The target must attempt a DC 15 Fortitude save to avoid sneezing. On a failed save, the creature sneezes uncontrollably, becoming slowed 1 for 1 round. On a critical failure, the creature is instead slowed 1 for 3 rounds.",
